<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM4.3.1">
<l>uruppiṇi naṅkaitaṉṉai mīṭpāṉtoṭarn tōṭiceṉṟa</l>
<l>vuruppaṉai yōṭṭikoṇṭiṭ ṭuṟaittiṭṭu ṟaippaṉmalai</l>
<l>poruppiṭaik koṉṟainiṉṟu muṟiyāḻiyuṅ kācuṅkoṇṭu</l>
<l>viruppoṭu poṉvaḻaṅkum viyaṉmāliruñ cōlaiyatē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The mountain of him who rebuked and disgraced Rukmaṉ,</l>
<l rend="indent">who went running after [him]</l>
<l rend="indent">in order to return the lady Rukmiṇī,</l>
<l rend="indent">[and] drove [him] off,</l>
<l>that is the vast Māliruñcōlai where the Koṉṟai tree,</l>
<l rend="indent">standing on the mountain,</l>
<l rend="indent">lovingly gives golden rings and coins of leaves.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
